{"tid":1523993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［901入機場］核爆！唔使講野，入機場哂冷","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:46:32.000Z","uid":199911,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"994df03e3df37fac9f2bdf097718ef17c0860281","tid":1523993,"uid":199911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:16.000Z","msg":"一人一Post 洗爆連登時事台 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：［901入機場］核爆！唔使講野，入機場哂冷<br />\n<br />\n繼「黑警還眼」後<br />\n901統一口號「黑警恐襲」「黑警放火」<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n見者Copy內容開新Post洗版，唔開Post自己檢討一下良心仲係唔係到！<br />\n<br />\n出完貼要自推10下，見到其他都推下，回post都要post上面"},{"pid":"738e287358e6bfa2d19b85396160a82211e65348","tid":1523993,"uid":199911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:34.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"2ff9f46cccbbb726fee4d619d47a501cbe8abdc8","tid":1523993,"uid":8730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u2DpW54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu2DpW54.jpg&h=aff9aac3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47e780d17fda2ec5d048637c2a24318fccba7af9","tid":1523993,"uid":199911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:53.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"d731c4423afbcfb1ce89611da51070eff0be76bb","tid":1523993,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:54.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2